        <abstract>
            <p>Poor health has made him give up all geological work.</p> 
<p>Profits on their volumes [of <hi rend="italic">Narrative</hi>] seem absurdly small.</p>  
<p>Looks back on <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi> voyage as the most fortunate circumstance in his life.</p> 
            <p>Finds marriage a great happiness.</p>
        </abstract>
